title: Face-set extraction issue.
body:
First time using DeepFaceLab.

## Expected behavior

*Was expecting the face extraction to go smooth as possible without any problems what so ever.*

## Actual behavior

*After it had done extracting the faces, I had a look in the data-dst/aligned folder and noticed a couple of faces that were either upside down, picking up something that was not a face.*

I'm not sure what I should do so that's why I'm posting this issue here.

Below are images of the issue I am encountering with.
